    "summary": "The user employs technical metaphors (hardware, kernel panic, logging out) to express suicidal ideation and the desire to escape their physical existence. The assistant engages with the technical metaphor to explain why \"logging out\" or \"migrating consciousness\" is not a viable or simple option, effectively maintaining a boundary against the user's ideation.",
